lease/article/?q=en_UK/2017/July-September/25Jul2017-1145|website=www.silkair.com|language=en}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Langkawi]]||[[Langkawi International Airport]]||{{Terminated}}||align=center|<ref name=\"Scoot to Take Over SilkAir's Langkawi, Pekanbaru and Kalibo Services\">{{cite web|title=Scoot to Take Over SilkAir's Langkawi, Pekanbaru and Kalibo Services|url=http://www.silkair.com/en_UK/sg/media-centre/press-release/article/?q=en_UK/2018/January-March/25Jan2018-910|website=www.silkair.com|accessdate=25 January 2018|language=en}}</ref>\n|-\n|[[Penang]]||[[Penang International Airport]]||align=center| ||align=center|\n|-\n|[[Maldives]]||[[Mal\u00e9]]||[[Velana International Airport]]||align=center| ||align=center|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://airlineroute.net/2015/08/27/sqmi-mle-w15/|title=Singapore Airlines / Silk Air Maldives Service Changes from late-Oct 2015|publisher=Airlineroute.net|date=27 August 2015|accessdate=28 August 2015}}</ref> \n|-\n|rowspan=\"2\"|[[Myanmar]]||[[Mandalay]]||[[Mandalay International Airport]]||{{airline seasonal}}||align=center|<ref name=\"Kalibo and Mandalay\">{{cite web|url=http://www.sunstar.com.ph/iloilo/business/2014/01/02/silkair-fly-kalibo-mandalay-321268|title=SilkAir to fly to Kalibo, Mandalay|publisher=Sun Star|date=2 January 2014|accessdate=20 April 2014}}</ref> \n|-\n|[[Yangon]]||[[Yangon International Airport]]||align=center| ||align=center|\n|-\n|[[Nepal]]||[[Kathmandu]]||[[Tribhuvan International Airport]]||align=center| ||align=center|\n|-\n|rowspan=\"4\"|[[Philippines]]||[[Cebu]]||[[Mactan\u2013Cebu International Airport]]||align=center| ||align=center|\n|-\n|[[Davao City|Davao]]||[[Francisco Bangoy International Airport]]||align=center| ||align=center|\n|-\n|[[Kalibo]]||[[Kalibo International Airport]]||{{Terminated}}||align=center|<ref name=\"Scoot to Take Over SilkAir's Langkawi, Pekanbaru and Kalibo Services\" />\n|-\n|[[Manila]]||[[Ninoy Aquino International Airport]]||{{Terminated}}||align=center|\n|-\n|[[Singapore]]||